description:
Glad Food Storage Containers, Small Bowl, are a convenient and secure way to store or transport food while sealing in freshness. Lids easily snap on creating a tight seal and preventing messy spills. Reusable, but also extra sturdy, these containers can be used for keeping fruit salad for a picnic or saving soup in the freezer. Glad Food Storage Containers are just the right size for storing dinner or for sending leftovers home with party guests. BPA free and microwave safe, you can safely heat food in these containers. Clean up is quick and easy because they are dishwasher safe. When you use Glad, you know your food is receiving quality protection.


Directions: Wash food containers before use. Lock lids together for easy storage by placing one lid on a flat surface and a second lid of the same shape on top. Gently press down on the button in the center of the top lid until you feel the two lids connect. Repeat this process to lock additional lids onto the stack.

Ingredients: BPA free

Warnings: Glad food containers should not be used for boiling, in ovens, under broilers or on the stove top. Before microwaving, remove lid and place loosely on top to vent. Handle all hot containers with care.
